1 """
2 This package manipulates a ROS network so that it provides an enviornment to
3 train an AI. In short, it uses the sim time mechanism used to replay bag files
4 to mess with how time progresses, so that an arbitrary ROS network can be used
5 as an environment, specifically, an OpenAI Gym environment.
6 
7 This can be used for both training and evaluation purposes. When training, it
8 manipulates time so that the network gets what it needs. It evaluation, it
9 runs the network as fast as real time is progressing.
